              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After completing Death Plateau",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hi!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "I heard about what you did, thank you!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hi!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "The White Knights are still going to take over."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hi!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "I hear the Imperial Guard are preparing an attack!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hi!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Thank you so much!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hi!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Surely we are safe now!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After completing A Tale of Two Cats and losing the Catspeak amulet (e)",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I've lost my enchanted Amulet of Catspeak."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "This can be rectified, simply bring me another Amulet of Catspeak and five death runes and I will enchant it for you."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I don't have the five death runes on me."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Come back to me when you have them."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I have the runes but don't have the amulet on me."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Bring me the amulet and I will enchant it for you."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I have the death runes with me now."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Good. Give me the amulet so that I may perform the enchantment."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "Using the enchanted amulet is easy; open up the amulet and you'll see a cat's face, use the whiskers to rotate the cats nose. You'll see the nose move and the new direction highlighted. When the nose points in the"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "direction that Bob is in, the eyes will light up and the mouth will open. You'll need to head in that direction and then check the direction again. If you are very close to Bob then the eyes and mouth will animate no"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Hild",
                  "text": "matter which way the nose is pointing. That's all there is to it, good luck!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}